=Episode 19=

19
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:23,590
Long live Your Grace!

20
00:01:24,710 --> 00:01:26,590
General Zhao Ming, please rise.

21
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:30,070
May I ask

22
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:32,480
why Your Grace summoned me for today?

23
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:35,590
It's a matter of great regret and misfortune.

24
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:38,120
I've summoned you today, General,

25
00:01:38,350 --> 00:01:40,590
to discuss the Crown Prince.

26
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:42,590
I can't bear to see

27
00:01:42,870 --> 00:01:45,760
the Crown Prince's hands
stained with blood.

28
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,480
What do you mean, Your Grace?

29
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,040
I don't understand.

30
00:01:50,070 --> 00:01:52,150
Although the Crown Prince
is not my biological son,

31
00:01:52,430 --> 00:01:54,120
I've watched him grow up

32
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:56,070
and he calls me Mother.

33
00:01:56,510 --> 00:01:57,760
As his mother,

34
00:01:58,120 --> 00:02:00,870
I can't just stand by
and watch him make a mistake.

35
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,920
I still don't understand
what Your Grace means.

36
00:02:08,870 --> 00:02:09,710
General Zhao,

37
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,870
do you remember the Chief
by the Crown Prince's side,

38
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,560
a woman surnamed Gu?

39
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,240
His Highness said she was unwell

40
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,120
and has returned to her hometown.

41
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:24,680
If she truly has returned home,
that's it.

42
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,590
But I've heard

43
00:02:26,750 --> 00:02:28,150
that this palace maid named Gu

44
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,520
has attempted to assassinate
the Crown Prince multiple times

45
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,240
and is no longer tolerated by him.

46
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:35,080
She's to be executed tonight.

47
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:41,800
Your sister is about
to marry the Crown Prince,

48
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,430
and is surely more aware of his actions

49
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:45,680
than I, his mother.

50
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,430
Why not ask her

51
00:02:47,710 --> 00:02:48,800
what she thinks?

52
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,680
I take my leave.

53
00:02:58,380 --> 00:02:59,420
(The Defender Duke's Mansion)

54
00:02:59,430 --> 00:03:01,280
Sister, what's going on?

55
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:02,630
Why won't you tell me?

56
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,240
Brother,

57
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,680
I...

58
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,840
Yao is in grave danger,

59
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:12,430
and you grew up with her.

60
00:03:12,710 --> 00:03:14,120
Can you really bear to see her die?

61
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:15,840
Brother,

62
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:18,590
I'm sorry.

63
00:03:18,710 --> 00:03:20,710
Sister, what happened?

64
00:03:21,630 --> 00:03:22,680
I didn't want this.

65
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,560
I really didn't want this.

66
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,520
I didn't know the Crown Prince

67
00:03:26,630 --> 00:03:28,360
had made her lose her memory.

68
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,470
I thought she was pretending.

69
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:31,870
I really didn't know,

70
00:03:32,710 --> 00:03:33,590
so I...

71
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,240
Lost her memory?

72
00:03:36,910 --> 00:03:37,750
What did you do?

73
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:42,030
I told her everything.

74
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:45,270
Brother,

75
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:49,030
I never thought the Crown Prince
would kill Sister Yao.

76
00:03:49,710 --> 00:03:51,680
I didn't want things
to turn out this way.

77
00:03:52,150 --> 00:03:52,990
Brother,

78
00:03:53,750 --> 00:03:54,870
it was not intentional.

79
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,120
I understand now.

80
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:58,470
Brother!

81
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,680
General.

82
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:08,470
Have you found out anything?

83
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:10,430
Reporting to the General,

84
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:12,280
