on the surface,

85
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,430
but our spies report

86
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:17,510
that the Crown Prince does plan
to execute a traitor tonight.

87
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:31,830
Notify all the brothers,

88
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,430
come with me tonight.

89
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:34,840
Yes.

90
00:04:36,020 --> 00:04:39,500
(Command)

91
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,310
You say the Defender Northern Army
is showing signs of movement?

92
00:04:57,510 --> 00:04:59,390
That's right.

93
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:00,440
We've confirmed the information.

94
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,630
