102
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,600
As for Zhao Ming,

103
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:24,950
let's see how far he gets.

104
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,080
Yes.

105
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,310
