133
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:24,990
Anyone who trespasses
into the Eastern Palace will be killed!

134
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:29,160
Your Highness, General Zhao Ming
has entered Miss Gu's room with his men.

135
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,440
