143
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,760
Quick!

144
00:08:05,310 --> 00:08:06,150
Stop!

145
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,840
- Miss Gu!
- Move aside!

146
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,320
Miss Gu,

147
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:16,270
His Highness has ordered

148
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:17,560
